OL,3,CBBC launches workplace culture review
OL,4,Cfollowing string of star scandals
OL,6,FThe BBC has launched an independent
OL,7,Freview into workplace culture at the
OL,8,Fcorporation following a string of star-
OL,9,Frelated scandals.
OL,11,FIt will also look into how the BBC can
OL,12,Fdeal with instances of power abuse
OL,13,Fwhen they are identified.
OL,15,FIt follows the sentencing of disgraced
OL,16,Fformer BBC presenter Huw Edwards to
OL,17,Fsix months imprisonment, suspended for
OL,18,Ftwo years, after pleading guilty to
OL,19,Faccessing indecent images of children
OL,20,Fas young as seven.
