OL,3,CBBC launches workplace culture review
OL,4,Cfollowing string of star scandals
OL,6,FAnd, the sacking of March of the Day
OL,7,Fand The One Show presented Jermaine
OL,8,FJenas, after he sent "inappropriate"
OL,9,Fmessages to two women he worked with.
OL,11,FBoth Edwards' conviction and Jenas'
OL,12,Fsacking came at a time when the BBC
OL,13,Fwas already under-fire over 'abuse'
OL,14,Fcomplaints aimed at Strictly Come
OL,15,FDancing star Giovanni Pernice.
OL,17,FIn an email to staff, BBC Chairman
OL,18,FSamir Shah said: "I cannot emphasise
OL,19,Fenough that I am fully committed to
OL,20,Ftackling inappropriate or abusive
OL,21,Fbehaviour.
