OL,3,CBBC launches workplace culture review
OL,4,Cfollowing string of star scandals
OL,6,F"For most of us it is a joy to work
OL,7,Ffor the BBC and that should be the
OL,8,Fcase for everyone. Nobody working in
OL,9,Fthe BBC should ever feel fear or worry
OL,10,Fwhile working here.
OL,12,F"What is clear to me is that we must
OL,13,Fensure the BBC is a safe, secure and
OL,14,Fwelcoming workplace for everyone."
